            <title>[PIG-2191] Reduce amount of log spam generated by UDFs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2191</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Many builtin UDFs use log.warn instead of warn() to report warnings. This can produce an inordinate and unneeded amount of error logging. The warn() method is provided to aggregate that sort of thing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
